snippet.title: Metro.Siberia underground
snippet.description:
NEW GAME! From salomonsson.se

Title: Metro.Siberia underground.
Platform: Macromedia/Adobe Flash.
Description: Amazing retro soviet style gravity game! Use the space bar on your keyboard to directly adjust the thrust of the vehicle. Find the darkest and most powerful technical devices from this forgotten era!

Difficulty: 10 of 10
